parameters: \n<Man's voice>"Hey! Doctor!! Hurry up! Treat her quickly!"
--Doctors and medics are bustling about in a field hospital.

A man clad in knight's armor suddenly barges in, shouting
angrily yet carefully lays a woman down on a bed.
\n<Knight>"Stop dawdling! You lot, treat this person quickly!"

The intimidated doctors stop their work to surround the bed.
Upon seeing the woman lying there, they let out a gasp of
surprise.

\n<Doctors>"Impossible... This person is...!? You're joking, right!?
What in the world happened...!?"

\n<Knight>"What are you dilly-dallying for!? Treat this person at
once!!"
\n<Medic A>"Knight-sama, please step back! We'll take it from here...!"

The doctors and medics, with changed complexions, surround
the woman and begin examining her in a panic.

\n<Doctors>"The head injury is severe...! We need to stop the bleeding!
Bring more cloth! Can you hear me? Can you hear my voice!?
No response--!"

\n<Knight>"--You bastards! Do you understand what will happen if
something goes wrong with this person!?"
\n<Medic A>"Even if you say that! Please, just step back!"

\n<Doctor A>"...No good, we need the doctor... Call the medical
practitioner! At this point, only a medical spell can save
her!"

\n<Knight>"Damn it! Then hurry up and call them! Where is this medical
practitioner!?"
\n<Doctor B>"They're, uh, attending to another patient in the back!"

The knight rushes to the back of the field hospital at full
speed.
\n<Doctor A>"This is bad... her breathing is...!"
\n<Doctor B>"Stay calm! Doctor! Please come quickly, Doctor--!!"

The doctors continue to administer desperate treatment while
calling out.

However, the woman's breathing gradually becomes more
ragged--
And then, she lets out one large breath.
